I attended the "Computer Network" Course of National Taiwan University opened by Prof.Polly Huang(黃寶儀) in 2021 fall.We learnt to use "Go language" through PA1 to PA9 for further comprehension in Computer Network.
All requirements and tutorial are on the course webpage: 
